通安全隐患。 查获当日下午，大队第一时间通知当事人骆某某的监护人及车辆所有人到队配合调查处理。同时，民警对骆某某及其监护人进行批评教育。 （来源 封面新闻）12 岁男孩独自驾车高速狂飙 6 小时，被查时谎称：「我有矮小症！」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1ead7188dd52d46403e5a85cf961528_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2051001274779301605"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4oD84uLF0tIjEAMaCTEyMDAzOTIyOSCpg8/RBjAAOKcBQAZyEzIwNTEwMDEyNzQ3NzkzMDE2MDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1781972316.842111", "card_id": "Q_2050956959000565700", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 351}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "演员吴倩自曝被父亲打掉牙齿不敢吐，掌掴真能直接打掉牙齿吗？如何看待这种经历对人的影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "演员吴倩在近期采访中谈及原生家庭，自曝童年因逗弄邻居家的小狗被咬伤后，遭父亲掌掴导致牙齿脱落，因为害怕，她不敢把牙齿吐出来，而是直接吞了下去。 为弥补童年缺憾，会对女儿频繁表达爱意。对于「复婚」传闻，吴倩：没有复婚。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d78674187efe2b229fdf8dac2412cac3_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "81 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2050956959000565700"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI4oD84uLF0tIjEAMaCTEyMDAzNzE0OCDjsM7RBjAAOJ8EQAdyEzIwNTA5NTY5NTkwMDA1NjU3MDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1781972316.842692", "card_id": "Q_2051069358131115104", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 94}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待陈建斌蒋勤勤儿子不进娱乐圈，被加州大学伯克利分校录取？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "陈建斌蒋勤勤儿子高中毕业，被加州大学伯克利分校录取。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6232d96546060d687c0